reviewText: Liked it a lot. typical B movie
My family and I enjoyed watching this movie. We find plague type insect movies to be mindless fun.  This movie was quite entertaining and worth buying.  Was in good condition, also
What can I say it's a B grade horror flick. If you are not looking for award winning scripts, sit back, grab the popcorn and have fun. D
